  "A tax on real estate property owned during your lifetime": "",
  "A tax on home sales profits": "",
  "A tax paid by heirs on any inheritance they receive": "",
  "The estate tax is levied on the total value of a deceased person's estate above the exemption amount. It is paid by the estate before assets are distributed to beneficiaries.": "",
  "What does 'regressive tax' mean?": "",
  "A tax that takes a larger percentage of income from low-income earners than from high-income earners": "",
  "A tax that decreases as income increases": "",
  "A tax that is gradually phased out over time": "",
  "A tax that only applies to wealthy individuals": "",
